stories_text_raw:
As a Cluster administrator, I want to process deletions for a specific date, so that I can maintain data consistency.
As a Cluster administrator, I want to redesign the Resources page, so that users have an improved experience.
As a Cluster administrator, I want to report user testing results, so that I can identify areas for improvement.
As a Cluster administrator, I want to update SQL codes for clarity, so that the database is more maintainable.
As a Cluster administrator, I want to add PPoPCode cases to derivation logic, so that data quality is improved.
As a Cluster administrator, I want to derive the FundingAgencyCode, so that data is complete and accurate.
As a UI designer, I want to move to the next round of page edits, so that the design process can proceed efficiently.
As a developer, I want to add updates to the FABS submission, so that the system is up-to-date.
As a developer, I want to add GTAS window data to the database, so that the system has the latest information.
As a developer, I want to update the FABS sample file, so that it reflects the current system state.
As an agency user, I want to access published FABS files, so that I can view the latest data.
As an agency user, I want to get file-level error information, so that I can troubleshoot issues.
As a FABS user, I want to download uploaded FABS files, so that I can access the data I need.
As a FABS user, I want to see correct status labels on the Submission Dashboard, so that I can track the status of my submissions.
As a broker user, I want to help create content mockups, so that I can contribute to the design process.
As a broker user, I want to submit records for individual recipients, so that I can fulfill my responsibilities.
